                      Systems Acquisition Office Header

                     Financial Planning & Control Staff

                               [blueline.gif]

   The Financial Planning and Control (FPC) Staff is responsible for
   integrating the financial aspects of all Systems Acquisition Office
   programs. FPC serves as the focal point for budget formulation and
   execution, planning and policy, resource management, matrix support,
   cost baselining, and financial profile activities.

